name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Big Trezz
description:
Beastmaster Collection Series 1

Big Trezz was recruited onto the strikeforce after being an intergalactic mercenary. Many mistake his gruff nature and sarcastic personality as being a bit of an asshole but he's never left a teammate behind. He's also the first to step in front of a bullet to protect his friends. His scars prove his determination to be a protector.His axe edges are searing hot like molten lava which can cut through anything.
